            "title": "警搜元朗天水圍3住宅單位 檢$21萬毒品包括太空油毒品煙彈 5人被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/5e2383a0e49e242ff9e0a30c20f93c4a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031320291974683.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>元朗警區反三合會行動組第一隊人員根據線報及經深入調查，昨日（12日）下午突擊搜查3個分別位於天水圍及元朗的住宅單位，共檢獲589粒懷疑含有液態依托咪酯（俗稱「太空油毒品」）的電子煙彈、少量懷疑「冰」毒、少量懷疑大麻、79枝懷疑電子煙槍及約9000元現金。<br/>\n<br/>\n行動中，警方檢獲的毒品市值約21萬元。經調查後，人員拘捕4名本地女子及1名本地男子，他們年齡介乎21至43歲，涉嫌「販運危險藥物」及「管有危險藥物」，他們現正被扣留調查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135818/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方拘捕5人涉嫌「販運危險藥物」及「管有危險藥物」。警方提供\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4ff9e7dbc90572fa9a9f061dfaae7849/2025-03/MIU_Trafficking_in_DD_DATS_1_YLDIST.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方拘捕5人涉嫌「販運危險藥物」及「管有危險藥物」。警方提供\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
