            "title": "「Bonne Maman」兩款果醬及塗抹醬或含霉菌  有進口香港  食安中心籲勿食用",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"「Bonne Maman」兩款果醬及塗抹醬或含霉菌  有進口香港  食安中心籲勿食用\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/fd4c89ba20970114b15d60b87c56914f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031320161633989.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">「Bonne Maman」兩款果醬及塗抹醬或含霉菌  有進口香港  食安中心籲勿食用</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>法國「Bonne Maman」兩款樽裝果醬及塗抹醬產品可能含霉菌。食環署食物安全中心已確定有關進口商曾進口受影響批次的有關產品到港，呼籲市民不要食用，業界如持有受影響批次的產品，應立即停止使用或出售。\n\n</p>\n<p>產品資料如下：<br/>\n<br/>\n產品名稱：Chestnut Cream<br/>\n品牌：Bonne Maman<br/>\n來源地：法國<br/>\n重量：225克<br/>\n此日期前最佳：2026年6月30日<br/>\n編碼：45108082<br/>\n進口商：Getz Bros. &amp; Co.（Hong Kong）Limited<br/>\n<br/>\n產品名稱：Fig Jam<br/>\n品牌：Bonne Maman<br/>\n來源地：法國<br/>\n重量：225克<br/>\n此日期前最佳：2026年5月31日<br/>\n編碼：45119668<br/>\n進口商：Getz Bros. &amp; Co.（Hong Kong）Limited\n\n</p>\n<p>中心得悉日本厚生勞動省和澳門食品安全廳的通告，指有關產品可能含霉菌，正進行回收。該進口商已按中心指示將受影響產品停售和下架，並展開回收。市民欲查詢有關產品的回收事宜，可於辦公時間致電該進口商熱線3126 2303。<br/>\n<br/>\n發言人說，市民應停止食用受影響產品，如食用有關產品後感到不適，應盡快求醫。業界亦應立即停止使用或出售有關產品。中心已就事件通知業界，並繼續跟進事件和採取適當行動。調查仍然繼續。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057995/即時-港聞-Bonne-Maman-兩款果醬及塗抹醬或含霉菌-有進口香港-食安中心籲勿食用",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-13 20:26:08",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "贖夢｜劉俊謙雙腳纏鉛營造下沉效果 水中演戲加連番掙扎險窒息",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"贖夢｜劉俊謙雙腳纏鉛營造下沉效果 水中演戲加連番掙扎險窒息\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/1904e638d1eb794e5e3514823f3ff551/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031320080487528.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">贖夢｜劉俊謙雙腳纏鉛營造下沉效果 水中演戲加連番掙扎險窒息</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>張家輝自編自導自演新作《贖夢》，所有演員都為他拼命、忘我演出，陳法拉在預告片中面目掙擰的瘋癲演出，被網民冠以「陳法癲」稱號，令人心寒；而另一位主演劉俊謙也如是，飾演精神科文醫生的他，不斷陷入不安和困惑夢境之中，拍攝過程也經過幾番掙扎，其中一場水底戲更令他唞不過氣來，絕對是一次賭命演出。\n\n</p><h2>劉俊謙第一次拍潛水戲</h2>\n<p>電影公司特別安排潛水教練在泳池為阿謙實地教學，雖然他小時候學過游水，但跟潛水又是兩回事，阿謙有所領會地說：「水底閉氣和呼吸，再一下子浮上水面，很難回到氣，真的需要不斷練習。教練還要在我一對腳加上鉛，以營造往下沉的效果，所以有一定難度。」在潛水教練指導下，阿謙亦掌握到相關的基本技能，正式拍攝當晚使出渾身解數。拍攝當晚正是除夕夜，氣溫驟降，劇組又未及準備暖水，但都未有影晌阿謙賣命演出，完成演出後他仍嫌自己在水底的表情不夠好，連導演家輝都讚阿謙對工作的認真態度不可多得。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135077/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉俊謙除夕捱凍拍水底戲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e875b4179c7d298892bcd1c842bc2090/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_15_00_03_1__0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉俊謙除夕捱凍拍水底戲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135057/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"《贖夢》由張家輝（右）自編自導自演。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3b8aa4e647dd7ee2e29adb4deab019cd/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_15_00_02_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《贖夢》由張家輝（右）自編自導自演。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135058/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"張家輝仲唱埋《贖夢》主題曲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1f5cb4148e359a23583dde7702dc2e58/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_15_00_02_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        張家輝仲唱埋《贖夢》主題曲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135059/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"事前劉俊謙為《贖夢》接受水底訓練。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/afcd0632edafe58746cdbc6fc39d0bb3/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_15_00_02.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        事前劉俊謙為《贖夢》接受水底訓練。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135063/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉俊謙小時候學過游水，稱跟潛水是兩回事。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/72030eb2e97a312677e5bfb56ac1a3b7/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_15_00_03.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉俊謙小時候學過游水，稱跟潛水是兩回事。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135064/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉俊謙拍這場落水戲做足安全同保護措施。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/96b29e18965c2a90f4392ab1407571f5/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_15_00_04_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉俊謙拍這場落水戲做足安全同保護措施。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135066/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉俊謙上水即飲水。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cbab498ac6a6dd48935c12f6bc5c59d7/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_15_00_04_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉俊謙上水即飲水。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135067/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉俊謙十分專注於這場落水戲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6d7a807b428e47de66db368e6a566792/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_15_00_04_4_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉俊謙十分專注於這場落水戲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135068/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"教練從旁協助劉俊謙。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/37bbef59ab94a53c969d0ba56e5c8611/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_15_00_04.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        教練從旁協助劉俊謙。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135069/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉俊謙在正式拍攝前試位。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/21427e80706e62b482db1bfe40cfd3b9/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_15_00_05_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉俊謙在正式拍攝前試位。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135072/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉俊謙上水，慢慢回過神來。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ed6195c6c8c3499339a0fe20b6deae3a/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_15_00_05.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉俊謙上水，慢慢回過神來。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135074/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"張家輝十分欣賞劉俊謙的專業態度。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7b8d1f3324f4d1b28a5f15a7b0638f06/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_15_00_06_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        張家輝十分欣賞劉俊謙的專業態度。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135075/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉俊謙作事前訓練，一絲不苟。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dc50fbacc32d2a58795d630e93db1cfb/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_15_00_06_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉俊謙作事前訓練，一絲不苟。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>劉俊謙幾乎窒息</h2>\n<p>至於阿謙為拍這場夢境中水底掙扎戲，來來回回由水面跳落泳池水底不下數次，他表示：「我是第一次拍水底戲，氣溫突然聚下降，又沒有暖水，這也是預料不到的。在水底演戲，連番掙扎動作，還要加上臉部表情配合，真不容易，不過最辛苦一刻是上水的一刻，全身盡濕，必須要工作人員拉我才夠力上水；而每次上水也得吸氧氣，有一刻真的呼吸不到。奈何又不能待在水中演戲太久，怕缺氧。幸好沒等到天亮便完成整場戲，好一個難忘的除夕夜。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
